			<div class="article-correspondence layout-item fill-pattern-light">
		<div class="layout-item-intro">
			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="1284">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>Elizabeth Tibbetts&rsquo;s essay &ldquo;<a href="/article/4465">The Best Part</a>&rdquo; [October 2010] reminded me of the time I horrified my friends by telling them that one of my family&rsquo;s holiday traditions was to eat deer heart on Christmas Eve. They thought I was kidding until I provided them with the gory details.</p>

<p>My father and his father were both responsible hunters, never taking more than they could use and sharing the venison and hides with other hunters and their families. But the heart always belonged to the man who&rsquo;d killed the deer. When that was my father, he waited until Christmas Eve to offer up to us what he considered the best part.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Dianne C. Grove<br>Roswell, Georgia</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

					</div>

			</div>
    
		<div class="article-correspondence-cta">
		<div class="cta cta-l1" data-url="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">
			<div class="cta-intro">
				<h5 class="cta-title alt-ff">Thinking about writing us a letter?</h5>
				<p class="cta-text">Give in to the temptation. We love getting mail. <br><span class="xsmall">(Of course, we reserve the right to edit.)</span></p>
			</div>
			<a href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor" class="cta-button b b-4 b-padding-tight small" data-label="Write Us A Letter!">Write Us A Letter!</a>
